gscope (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Namespace isolation (PID, NET, MNT, UTS, IPC, USER, CGROUP)
  * Cgroup v2 resource limits
  * OverlayFS with pivot_root
  * seccomp-bpf syscall filtering (40+ blocked)
  * Netlink networking (bridge, veth, IP, routing)
  * Template executor (JSON config provisioning)
  * gscopectl CLI tool
  * Python bindings

 -- Gritiva <dev@gritiva.com>  Thu, 10 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000
